Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:12.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I step around I hear the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,C-clip a clopping' up and down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:22.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The shuffl~in' of hooves it surely proves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:25.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I'll see you 'fore the day's complete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:31.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What is this wonderful feel~ing~ in my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:38.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had it before I got up~ and outta bed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just wanna wear a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And come find you for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The colors all so vivid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:53.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our friends so green and livid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we touched I felt my skin could melt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I don't want you to quit it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:57.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Two years of courtship passed in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Canterlot wed~ding bells will ring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:05.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But now I need you I'm rackin' my brain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:09.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I can't think of any girl's names
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:16.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we step around we hear the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of little laugher chasin' butterflies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:25.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Round the sand and trees please let me be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Here forever under these blue skies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:35.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What is this wonderful feeling in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:42.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Could it be our whole life's about to start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And you're as content as me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In our small house by~ the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:53.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now that two's become a three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:03:01.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You and me and~ Ellie Bean